title: CROCHET - Interweave Crochet 2005-2014 (not all years complete)
description:
Issues of the magazine Interweave Crochet, from 2005 to 2014, but not all of them. For some years I have only two issues, for some I have three issues... Because I have painstakingly hunted for them all over the web. In some cases I have edited them, cleaned up watermarks or dark blotches etc... Not in all, though. 
Included is the book "The Best of Interweave Crochet" (edited by Marcy Smith), including 20 unique crochet patterns. 

P.S. I'm in Europe, and I can only seed at night. So don't start complaining if you don't get it immediately.
